snippet.title: Fall Guys Season 5 Exclusive Reveal!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Fall Guys Season 5 Reveal!

In this special event, we'll be showing off our brand new cinematic trailer, delving into what secrets the latest Fame Path holders, and taking an in-depth look at some of Season 5's new rounds!

We'll also be taking a bit of time to chat with the Fall Guys Development team about their time working on the newest update.
